title: Cinematic Titanic - Legacy of Blood
description:
Yet another offering from the folks at Cinematic Titanic. This is the video file only. No need to download the massive DVD file (complete with anti-rifftrax and anti-Bush propaganda, oddly enough). Enjoy!


------------------------------------------------------------------------


The Dean family patriarch has died and left a fortune to his children and servants. The occasion soon turns grim when they discover they must all must spend an entire week at the family estate ? together. It?s all the same old family routine: backbiting, billiards, rumors and innuendo, canings, pantsuits and ham ? until one by one, they start turning up dead. 


It's like high school... with your family! 
It's like Deliverance...with your family! 
It's like a family reunion...with your family! 
It's like nothing you've ever seen before.
